{"id":"82447aa31d2b2b609e1007c06a11e52c45de8bd7c42110b76233c5db33c0725a","item_id":"5cec499585:0","text":"在 Blender 中开始使用 Stylized Looks 渲染非常直接，只需要几个简单步骤。"}
{"id":"ed7d3aad201f4f0d26b4e6c297f905254181a8ff5a323ca588c86e96ea6ef6be","item_id":"5cec499585:1","text":"RenderMan Materials（RenderMan 材质）"}
{"id":"80adcd8416e726968666a37ef3782d5bdd737ebef2ce577b693d857af057bc7d","item_id":"5cec499585:2","text":"在使用 Stylized Looks 渲染前，请确认已向场景添加灯光，并已为对象附加 RenderMan 材质。"}
{"id":"816b6f7e1e4f28eb5cc6897d9925be3c7eb098f72a1366760bd9a68acaa8209f","item_id":"5cec499585:3","text":"在 viewport（视口）中右键点击并选择"}
{"id":"aa9f146c3d424a8c4b32f5ba83d79579f5d0892e81b6167e459582e2c1c8e4c4","item_id":"5cec499585:4","text":"RenderMan"}
{"id":"a88bd40266964df79b8ed4db5a39e6481deba65637f44d4d5b94fdb21e30ca49","item_id":"5cec499585:5","text":"Stylized（风格化）"}
{"id":"c64fb0872e9dfa5def312ae39f7bd36cf25c92470b60c42b704f2faba832cacb","item_id":"5cec499585:6","text":"Looks（外观）"}
{"id":"7f359436f2e7a543075082b2093fb9de4836e8791aa8b1c99dcfeb0998f7f199","item_id":"5cec499585:7","text":"Stylized Looks Editor（Stylized Looks 编辑器）"}
{"id":"615b896525006546798fef73abadd6a14e515657d9b934ac6963d2d37d02ef54","item_id":"5cec499585:8","text":"请先开启名为 Enable Stylized Looks 的开关。然后选择一个对象，并在 Attach Stylized Pattern（附加风格化图案）列表里选取 PxrStylizedControl 控制节点。"}
{"id":"b5df168408698494e1c53e61573833ef5f8df32d2387e90598894063564557d2","item_id":"5cec499585:9","text":"按下 OK 后，会创建所需的 PxrStylizedControl 节点，并将它们附加到机器人模型的 PxrSurface 上。"}
{"id":"c8b5311f6735c78e19ba86b3cb646915da3b9bb042f25c16710135f4cb69cea3","item_id":"5cec499585:10","text":"PxrStylizedControl 网络需要附加到场景中的每个对象，并允许对每个对象进行独立的着色控制。"}
{"id":"f45a3c38bb900f6bffcb2c96fe348414d1f9c0f0e23689fefc63c2d5e7a3661e","item_id":"5cec499585:11","text":"也可以通过选择一个对象，然后选择"}
{"id":"aa9f146c3d424a8c4b32f5ba83d79579f5d0892e81b6167e459582e2c1c8e4c4","item_id":"5cec499585:12","text":"RenderMan"}
{"id":"420e2d4380e8b92ab6a139872c3b38407f2b30f4843c9f97de79cd0f394925e6","item_id":"5cec499585:13","text":"Stylized Looks（风格化外观）"}
{"id":"81b3b65073911300398936b1f0044f39742d70f27ad1a7d0486cd4d6f1097406","item_id":"5cec499585:14","text":"Attach Stylized Pattern（附加风格化图案）"}
{"id":"d283ef081c33967f2c80c57228ce9f4d2e9836ee4afbe1e7303455a199d48d35","item_id":"5cec499585:15","text":"PxrStylizedControl"}
{"id":"225c3c1f76b6a370c7998c46ab2fdafcf4d8f67bec86deed54d42c80919019ba","item_id":"5cec499585:16","text":"使用 RenderMan Stylized Editor（RenderMan 风格化编辑器）后，现在可以开始添加 Stylized Filters（风格化滤镜），以创建你独特的 Stylized Look（风格化外观）。"}
{"id":"1a60e8d42195c49641837883bd102f057aef89356ffd47e4c6e2bcb3ec3a2d34","item_id":"5cec499585:17","text":"在此示例中，我们会添加排线滤镜 PxrStylizedHatching Filter（PxrStylizedHatching 滤镜）。"}
{"id":"311022306098026f00e319d45e37adf1aa587a39570cecda0c2612a4c4028943","item_id":"5cec499585:18","text":"现在启动 IPR，场景就会以 Stylized Looks 开始渲染。"}
{"id":"a872a13138607468e6494469d321623544f2f686bfea1860c66879b04732e36c","item_id":"5cec499585:19","text":"注意：在此示例中，默认设置已按如下方式调整："}
{"id":"4aa9868ce180102abbe3c24f4224a9f982379ccd371981b0bd6f641ff688e37b","item_id":"5cec499585:20","text":"a) Signal Energy From（信号能量来源）："}
{"id":"06242946da1f878f33747adcc8c1752247a03ca72211ecf4a3b9993883974e5d","item_id":"5cec499585:21","text":"Albedo AOV（反照率 AOV）"}
{"id":"b26640255f8897f991d1d531da7b6f050b19e0780189707a3d83c31299634801","item_id":"5cec499585:22","text":"b) Blending Mode（混合模式）："}
{"id":"ec0fad25382b164208db5569ef38152b17f88cea3df334667db69292a6a95f5d","item_id":"5cec499585:23","text":"Weighted（加权）"}
{"id":"61606943494c066f52d91098bfaf48be5ba999c49eb745c2a49921a7c6b30ced","item_id":"5cec499585:24","text":"c) Blend Black Darkest（黑色按最暗混合）："}
{"id":"e8a01133b1351e5fa434167135400d1998d3daa8ce74e3dd9bb57582fa4d7b97","item_id":"5cec499585:25","text":"ON（开启）"}
{"id":"dc8834927e52b749f7c0ae454a432626e57492f176bfef5839bf46ebe158df12","item_id":"5cec499585:26","text":"d) Projection（投影）："}
{"id":"6e56137e21d3222a2e3135fc3458286fc3fb6b2e2c679e9ae28db268fe982af7","item_id":"5cec499585:27","text":"Screen（屏幕）"}
{"id":"6f5377c880f3d41fcc91bb23698945286c97ec43067a49b003b81283a331208b","item_id":"5cec499585:28","text":"e) Hatching Frequency（排线频率）参数："}
{"id":"b3651eefac7726712a09619161eac077e54018c75d6c3695482d7b597d311479","item_id":"5cec499585:29","text":"现在你已经可以使用 Stylized Looks 渲染了！"}
{"id":"05447feb1d4948167a1ec8f391592287393f8de0a13ea03a54cbafde0d89a8d1","item_id":"5cec499585:30","text":"你的 NPR 创作之旅已经开始。不要忘记，Stylized Looks 的强大之处在于可以组合多种 Stylized Filters（风格化滤镜），创建你自己的独特风格和外观。"}
{"id":"ef6777086ff6f8afc2f900e348c44cac3a1beeac5d2d5ea7ff0c78d057559f81","item_id":"5cec499585:31","text":"Stylized Looks 还随附多个有趣的预设，帮助你快速开始。你可以在 RenderMan Preset Browser 中找到这些预设。"}
